      <title>加纳批准 13 名候选人参加 12 月总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/ghana-approves-13-candidates-for-december-s-presidential-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳选举委员会已经批准 13 名候选人参加该黄金和可可生产国即将举行的总统选举。]]></description>
