    <item>
      <title>纽约市市长亚当斯的庇护所主任谢弗被美国传唤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/nyc-mayor-adams-asylum-director-schaeffer-is-subpoenaed-by-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 领导的政府面临越来越多的调查之际，美国检察官已向纽约市庇护寻求者行动办公室主任莫莉·谢弗 (Molly Schaeffer) 发出了传票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/nyc-mayor-adams-asylum-director-schaeffer-is-subpoenaed-by-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 19:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港富豪黎智英的律师瞄准中国外交协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/hong-kong-tycoon-lai-s-lawyers-target-china-diplomatic-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港前传媒大亨黎智英的国际法律团队正在敦促美国和英国就释放黎智英达成协议，目前这位 70 岁老人根据北京实施的国家安全法接受的审判已进入最后时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/hong-kong-tycoon-lai-s-lawyers-target-china-diplomatic-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 19:21:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌如何垄断广告技术市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/how-google-allegedly-monopolized-the-ad-technology-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部在联邦反垄断审判中指控，谷歌通过限制或消除其客户（包括网站出版商和广告商）的选择，垄断了用于购买和销售在线展示广告的技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/how-google-allegedly-monopolized-the-ad-technology-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 18:50:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州因手工计票面临选举延迟的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/georgia-risks-election-delay-by-approving-hand-counting-of-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在佐治亚州这个关键的总统摇摆州提前投票开始前几周，佐治亚州选举委员会批准了一项有争议的新规定，要求该州每个投票站的所有选票都必须进行手工计票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/georgia-risks-election-delay-by-approving-hand-counting-of-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 18:28:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂夫·艾斯曼因发表“庆祝”加沙袭击事件被停职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/eisman-deletes-x-account-after-post-celebrating-attack-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽伯格伯曼 (Neuberger Berman) 高级投资组合经理史蒂夫艾斯曼 (Steve Eisman) 因在社交媒体上发表言论表示“庆祝”加沙巴勒斯坦人的死亡而被停职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/eisman-deletes-x-account-after-post-celebrating-attack-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 18:27:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登为何要提高特朗普对中国的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/china-tariffs-why-biden-is-doubling-down-on-trump-s-levies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登正在加大对中国产品的关税，以回应美国官员所称的不公平贸易行为，特别是在世界几大经济体争夺主导地位的战略领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/china-tariffs-why-biden-is-doubling-down-on-trump-s-levies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 19:18:00 GMT</pubDate>
